Paper: hep-th/9311023

Date: 1993-11-03

Title: Hot QCD

Comments: 20 pages

Journal-ref: Acta Phys.Polon. B25 (1994) 99-114

I discuss a comprehensive approach to the spacelike physics in hightemperature QCD in three dimensions. The approach makes use of dimensionalreduction. I suggest that this approach is useful for high temperature QCD infour dimensions.